item.title: CVE-2016-8721|2024-08-06T02:27:41.340Z -- moxa -- moxa%20awk-3131a%20wap
item.description: An exploitable OS Command Injection vulnerability exists in the web application 'ping' functionality of Moxa AWK-3131A Wireless Access Points running firmware 1.1. Specially crafted web form input can cause an OS Command Injection resulting in complete compromise of the vulnerable device. An attacker can exploit this vulnerability remotely.
